
langkah-langkah menjalankan project ini:
1. cek file go.mod ada apa engga kalo ga ada jalanin ini di terminal: 
	go mod init pestapi
2. terus jalanin perintah ini di terminal buat sinkroniasi module:
	go mod tidy

kalo aman jalanin perintah ini di terminal:
	= go run main.go
	nanti bakal muncul http://localhost:8080

kalo mau testing endpointnya bisa pake postman atau langsung di browser, 
ini beberapa endpoint yang bisa di coba:
- basic endpoint:
	- http://localhost:8080/pests
- menampilkan common name dari semua hama note: ini aku pake json yang dikirim all jadi masih 1 doang.
	- http://localhost:8080/pests/names
-basic search endpoint:
	- http://localhost:8080/pests/search?keyword=kopi
- Search Fast (Concurrency + Goroutine + Channel)
	- http://localhost:8080/pests/search-fast?keyword=wereng
- Get Pest by id - rekursi
	- http://localhost:8080/pests/get?id=1
- get pest by id (eror handling dengan func result)
	- eror ditemukan : http://localhost:8080/pests/get-func?id=1
	- eror tidak ditemukan :  http://localhost:8080/pests/get-func?id=99
- add pest (side effect handler)
	- http://localhost:8080/pests/add
	contoh:
	{
		"id": 2,
		"common_name": "Hama Uji Coba",
		"scientific_name": "Testus Testing",
		"pest_type": "Serangga",
		"affected_parts": ["Daun"],
		"description": "Hama untuk testing",
		"symptoms": ["Daun rusak"],
		"image_url": "http://example.com/test.jpg",
		"control_methods": {
			"organic": ["Semprot air"],
			"chemical": ["Insektisida test"]
		}
	}
- Pipeline (Map + Filter + Sort + Limit + Reduce)
	- default : http://localhost:8080/pests/pipeline
	- filter + limit : http://localhost:8080/pests/pipeline?type=fungi&limit=3
- stats reduce : http://localhost:8080/pests/stats
-immutable : http://localhost:8080/pests/immutable-demo
- pipeline advanced : http://localhost:8080/pests/pipeline-advanced?part=daun&type=serangga&limit=2
- filter by part : http://localhost:8080/pests/by-part?part=daun
- filter by type : http://localhost:8080/pests/by-type?type=serangga
- sort by common name : http://localhost:8080/pests/sorted?order=asc
- delete pest by id : http://localhost:8080/pests/delete?id=2
- update pest by id : http://localhost:8080/pests/update?id=3
- get random pest : http://localhost:8080/pests/random
- search by scientific name : http://localhost:8080/pests/search-scientific?keyword=hemileia
- stats full : http://localhost:8080/pests/stats/full
- search concurrent : http://localhost:8080/pests/search-concurrent?keyword=kopi
